original: Belfrage, Åke Lennart Knutsson, tandläkare, Växjö, f. 23/12/15 i Växjö av kapt. Kniut B. o. Vera Såndberg. G. 45 m. Vera-Mari Vange. — Studi-ex. 34, tandläk:ex. 39. Priv:prakt. i Växjö sed. 44.
translated: Belfrage, Åke Lennart Knutsson, dentist, born on December 23, 1915 in Växjö to Captain Knut B. and Vera Sandberg. Married in 1945 to Vera-Mari Vange. Completed his study examination in 1934 and his dental examination in 1939. Has been in private practice in Växjö since 1944.
